<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Welcome to Voice Data Collection Platform</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;'
  >
    <div
      style='background-color: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;'
    >
      <h1 style='margin: 0;'>Welcome!</h1>
    </div>
    <div
      style='background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;'
    >
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>Welcome to the Voice Data Collection Platform! We're excited to have
        you join our community of contributors.</p>
      <p>Your account has been successfully created. You can now start
        contributing to our linguistic data collection efforts.</p>
      <div style='text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;'>
        <a
          href='{{frontendUrl}}/dashboard'
          style='background-color: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;'
        >Get Started</a>
      </div>
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />The Voice Data Collection Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>